This sample shows how to call WithOperationPathParamAsync.

Uri endpoint = new Uri("<https://my-service.azure.com>");
MultipleClient client = new MultipleClient(endpoint);

Response response = await client.WithOperationPathParamAsync("<keyword>");

Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

This sample shows how to call WithOperationPathParamAsync with all parameters.

Uri endpoint = new Uri("<https://my-service.azure.com>");
MultipleClient client = new MultipleClient(endpoint);

Response response = await client.WithOperationPathParamAsync("<keyword>");

Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

